## 요약

| 메트릭 | 실제값 | 임계값 | 상태 | 변화 |
|--------|--------|--------|------|------|
{% for metric_name, mres in report.metrics.items() -%}
{%- set cfg = metrics_config[metric_name] if metric_name in metrics_config else none -%}
{%- set threshold_str = "%.4f"|format(cfg.threshold) if cfg else "-" -%}
{%- set status = "✅ PASS" if mres.passed else "❌ FAIL" -%}
{%- set change = "" -%}
{%- if previous_report -%}
  {%- set prev = previous_report.metrics[metric_name] if metric_name in previous_report.metrics else none -%}
  {%- if prev is not none -%}
    {%- set diff = mres.value - prev.value -%}
    {%- if diff > 0.001 -%}{%- set change = "📈 +" + "%.4f"|format(diff) -%}
    {%- elif diff < -0.001 -%}{%- set change = "📉 " + "%.4f"|format(diff) -%}
    {%- else -%}{%- set change = "➡️ 유지" -%}
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
| {{ metric_name }} | {{ "%.4f"|format(mres.value) }} | {{ threshold_str }} | {{ status }} | {{ change }} |
{% endfor %}

**전체 평가**: {% if report.overall_passed %}✅ **통과** ({{ report.passed_metrics }}/{{ report.total_metrics }}){% else %}❌ **미통과** ({{ report.passed_metrics }}/{{ report.total_metrics }}){% endif %}

